flowchart TD
    Run[Run request] --> Load[Load workflow from AWS RDB/RDS]
    Load --> Sort[Topological sort and execution context]
    Sort --> Node[Node execution loop]
    Node --> Templates[Resolve templates from upstream outputs]
    Templates --> RuntimeAI[Universal runtime AI value engine]
    RuntimeAI --> Validate[Pre-execution validation and audit]
    Validate --> Gate{Inputs valid?}
    Gate -->|No| Block[Fail before external provider call]
    Gate -->|Yes| Provider[Execute node adapter/provider call]
    Provider --> Output[Store output, status, timing, checkpoint]
    Output --> More{More nodes?}
    More -->|Yes| Node
    More -->|No| Done[Return final result and logs]
